{"tid":396544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌邨驚現胎盤？原來係凝固血塊","createTime":"2017-09-11T17:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T23:24:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eead813442cecec28ab1dc9b558b2a2282bdcd68","tid":396544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OVkCPsCMFFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOVkCPsCMFFE&d=Z5ot%2FCiM7rGSYmugGQuaDp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=5a95b84d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OVkCPsCMFFE</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌邨昨日發生胎盤驚魂。一名清潔女工發現電梯大堂有一個染血膠袋，袋內垃圾桶有凝固血塊及染血毛巾，她覺可疑報警。警員一度懷疑是人類胎盤，其後經調查，相信是大廈內一名男住客因腳部靜脈曲張血管爆裂，大量出血，其妹協助清理後將血塊及沾有血迹的物件棄掉，案件並無可疑。"},{"pid":"98d5d401de1c581c8440491f043440862af8351e","tid":396544,"uid":93839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T17:28:56.000Z","msg":"差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159cc63f15f33d1f71e811739ceb3b6882e108a4","tid":396544,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"睇到都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04dfb84fdad5ba1eed29e99b363e0c97b0e4876","tid":396544,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"重有哭聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae7644216e5f41e184cd2171cab32d453323beb","tid":396544,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T18:21:30.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6930d0da07490214cf5d2d76a3ca83b4ca56ac","tid":396544,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T2